<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>(平間)芹沢先生〜！</c>

00:14:27.165 --> 00:14:30.165 line:83% position:23.96% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>ん？なんじゃ やかましい。</c>

00:14:30.165 --> 00:14:33.858 line:72% position:28.12% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>いや どうも 八木家の幼子が</c>

00:14:30.165 --> 00:14:33.858 line:83% position:28.12% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>ゆうべ帰って来ず。</c>

00:14:33.858 --> 00:14:35.462 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>(芹沢)あ？</c>

00:14:35.462 --> 00:14:39.462 line:72% position:21.88% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>(平山)水田で死んでいるのが</c>

00:14:35.462 --> 00:14:39.462 line:83% position:34.38% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>見つかったようで。</c>

