00:15:38.231 --> 00:15:41.957 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>暇だな。</c>

00:15:41.957 --> 00:15:44.495 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>貴様 何か面白い絵でも描け。</c>

00:15:44.495 --> 00:15:47.726 line:83% position:30.21% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>本当に痛ましい事故でした。</c>

