00:17:42.396 --> 00:17:44.891 line:83% position:30.21% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>しかし これは どうして…。</c>

00:17:44.891 --> 00:17:48.924 line:72% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>理不尽としか言えません。</c>

00:17:44.891 --> 00:17:48.924 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>しかも…➡</c>

00:17:48.924 --> 00:17:52.660 line:72% position:28.12% align:start
