<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>誰にでも いつでも起こる。</c>

00:17:52.660 --> 00:17:56.660 line:83% position:44.79% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>土方。</c>

00:17:56.660 --> 00:18:00.396 line:72% position:34.38% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>一番きついのは</c>

00:17:56.660 --> 00:18:00.396 line:83% position:34.38% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>当事者達なんだ。</c>

00:18:00.396 --> 00:18:02.396 line:83% position:21.88% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>ただ耐え忍ぶしか ね〜だろ。</c>

