<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>お〜 蛍か。</c>

00:18:41.957 --> 00:18:46.627 line:72% position:21.88% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>そういえば 蛍には</c>

00:18:41.957 --> 00:18:46.627 line:83% position:21.88% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>亡くなった人の魂が宿る➡</c>

