<c.fgc-6.bgc-65>何としても</c>

00:19:10.462 --> 00:19:15.165 line:83% position:34.38% align:start
<c.fgc-6.bgc-65>生きてやるんだって光だ。</c>

00:19:15.165 --> 00:19:18.033 line:83% position:38.54% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>抱く感想は人それぞれ。</c>

00:19:18.033 --> 00:19:21.066 line:72% position:38.54% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>お菊ちゃんなら</c>

00:19:18.033 --> 00:19:21.066 line:83% position:38.54% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>どう言ったでしょうね。</c>

00:19:21.066 --> 00:19:25.561 line:72% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>お菊は昼寝ができないと</c>

00:19:21.066 --> 00:19:25.561 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>大声で駄々をこねた。</c>

00:19:25.561 --> 00:19:27.891 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>花や生き物が好きだった。➡</c>

00:19:27.891 --> 00:19:33.891 line:72% position:19.79% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>たくわんをよく噛まずに食べて</c>

00:19:27.891 --> 00:19:33.891 line:83% position:19.79% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>母親に怒られた。</c>

00:19:33.891 --> 00:19:37.363 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>生きるってのは長さじゃねぇ。</c>

00:19:37.363 --> 00:19:39.627 line:83% position:17.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>一生懸命 生きたんだ。</c>

00:19:39.627 --> 00:19:43.858 line:72% position:38.54% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>その光を</c>

00:19:39.627 --> 00:19:43.858 line:83% position:38.54% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>俺達は覚えておこうぜ。</c>

00:19:49.000 --> 00:19:51.462 line:83% position:38.54% align:start
