00:19:54.627 --> 00:19:58.066 line:83% position:42.71% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>飯も喉を通らんのう。</c>

00:19:58.066 --> 00:20:00.066 line:83% position:46.88% align:start
<c.fgc-7.bgc-65>して 芹沢先生は？</c>

00:20:00.066 --> 00:20:04.825 line:72% position:19.79% align:start
